<p>
Though this is a new service just launched, we have a large pool of candidates from both local school and international hotel schools. Apart from individual candidates, we are now in connect with many schools, like domestic Beijing Hospitality Institute, international Swiss School of Tourism & Hospitality, Republic Polytechnic Singapore, IUHB Germany etc. More connections with schools all around the globe including Switzerland, USA, UK, Netherlands, Spain, Hong Kong, Macao and domestic Mainland China are under negotiation and discussion. 
